b'Naniwa Yuukyouden': b'Taido Kaimon is the leader of the Kinshu Group ganster syndicate in Kansai region. His gang is a cluster of wisecracking madmen, eternally running into trouble with the law, each other, and the local girls who give as good as they get.\n\n(Source: The Anime Encyclopedia)'
